videos.description: After forcing a turnover Francis Alonso makes a great pass to Malik Massey who scores.
videos.headline: UNC Greensboro turns steal into layup

videos.description: David Burrell is all alone and puts down a big dunk for East Tennessee State.
videos.headline: Burrell punishes rim with powerful dunk

videos.description: James Dickey rises up and makes a powerful rejection for UNC Greensboro.
videos.headline: Dickey erases shot attempt with big block

videos.description: UNC Greensboro head coach Wes Miller is pleased with how his team is competing, but hopes the offensive improves in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Miller loves the way his team is fighting

videos.description: Isaiah Miller picks up a steal and takes it all the way to score for UNC Greensboro.
videos.headline: Miller turns defense into offense

videos.description: James Dickey blocks a layup attempt with authority for UNC Greensboro.
videos.headline: Dickey picks up another powerful block

videos.description: UNC Greensboro head coach Wes Miller gets emotional after his team defeats East Tennessee State to advance to the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Miller 'so proud' for his team to punch its ticket to Big Dance
